  "content:encoded": "<p><strong>Topics:</strong> <a title=\"Emotional Affairs\" href=\"https://newlife.com/?s=Emotional%20Affairs\">Emotional Affairs</a>, <a title=\"Lying\" href=\"https://newlife.com/?s=Lying\">Lying</a>, <a title=\"Forgiveness\" href=\"https://newlife.com/?s=Forgiveness\">Forgiveness</a>, <a title=\"Pornography\" href=\"https://newlife.com/?s=Pornography\">Pornography</a>, <a title=\"Adult Children\" href=\"https://newlife.com/?s=Adult%20Children\">Adult Children</a>, <a title=\"Abandonment\" href=\"https://newlife.com/?s=Abandonment\">Abandonment</a>, <a title=\"Father Issues\" href=\"https://newlife.com/?s=Father%20Issues\">Father Issues</a><br />\n<strong>Hosts:</strong> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/stevearterburn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Steve Arterburn</a>, <a href=\"http://twitter.com/drjillhubbard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dr. Jill Hubbard</a>, <a href=\"http://twitter.com/drjimburns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dr. Jim Burns</a></p>\n<p><strong>Caller Questions:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>I caught my wife sexting and lying about it; how do I forgive her? <a title=\"Tweet This\" href=\"http://twitter.com/?status=@NewLifeLive%20caller%20said%20%22I%20caught%20my%20wife%20sexting%20and%20lying%20about%20it--how%20do%20I%20forgive%20her?%22%20https://newlife.com/new-life-live-October-18-2022\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://newlife.com/wp-content/uploads/twitter.png\" alt=\"tweet this episode of New Life Live\" height=\"12px\" border=\"0\" /></a></li>\n<li>Like your first caller, my wife had affairs and my marriage was unable to be fixed. <a title=\"Tweet This\" href=\"http://twitter.com/?status=@NewLifeLive%20caller%20said%20%22Like%20your%20first%20caller,%20my%20wife%20had%20affairs%20and%20my%20marriage%20was%20unable%20to%20be%20fixed.%22%20https://newlife.com/new-life-live-October-18-2022\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://newlife.com/wp-content/uploads/twitter.png\" alt=\"tweet this episode of New Life Live\" height=\"12px\" border=\"0\" /></a></li>\n<li>I had a porn addiction, and reading <em>Every Young Man&#8217;s Battle</em> helped me to commit to making changes! <a title=\"Tweet This\" href=\"http://twitter.com/?status=@NewLifeLive%20caller%20said%20%22I%20had%20a%20porn%20addiction,%20and%20reading%20Every%20Young%20Man%27s%20Battle%20helped%20me%20to%20commit%20to%20making%20changes!%22%20https://newlife.com/new-life-live-October-18-2022\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://newlife.com/wp-content/uploads/twitter.png\" alt=\"tweet this episode of New Life Live\" height=\"12px\" border=\"0\" /></a></li>\n<li>My 22yo daughter gained eighty pounds since getting married, and I saw a half-empty vodka bottle. Where do I start with her without getting her upset? <a title=\"Tweet This\" href=\"http://twitter.com/?status=@NewLifeLive%20caller%20said%20%22My%2022yo%20daughter%20gained%20eighty%20pounds%20since%20getting%20married,%20and%20I%20saw%20a%20half-empty%20vodka%20bottle.%20Where%20do%20I%20start%20with%20her%20without%20getting%20her%20upset?%20%20%22%20https://newlife.com/new-life-live-October-18-2022\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://newlife.com/wp-content/uploads/twitter.png\" alt=\"tweet this episode of New Life Live\" height=\"12px\" border=\"0\" /></a></li>\n<li>I am an ecstatic new grandfather, and then hit an emotional pothole. Why is being abandoned by my dad coming up now? <a title=\"Tweet This\" href=\"http://twitter.com/?status=@NewLifeLive%20caller%20said%20%22I%20am%20an%20ecstatic%20new%20grandfather,%20and%20then%20hit%20an%20emotional%20pothole.%20Why%20is%20being%20abandoned%20by%20my%20dad%20coming%20up%20now?%22%20https://newlife.com/new-life-live-October-18-2022\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img src=\"https://newlife.com/wp-content/uploads/twitter.png\" alt=\"tweet this episode of New Life Live\" height=\"12px\" border=\"0\" /></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Suggested Resources:</strong><br />\n<a title=\"Life Recovery Bible\" href=\"https://store.newlife.com/search?searchText=Life%20Recovery%20Bible\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Life Recovery Bible</a><br />\n<a title=\"Life Recovery Workbook\" href=\"https://store.newlife.com/search?searchText=Life%20Recovery%20Workbook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Life Recovery Workbook</a><br />\n<a title=\"Every Young Mans Battle\" href=\"https://store.newlife.com/search?searchText=Every%20Young%20Mans%20Battle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Every Young Man&#8217;s Battle</a><br />\n<a title=\"Every Mans Bible\" href=\"https://store.newlife.com/search?searchText=Every%20Mans%20Bible\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Every Man&#8217;s Bible</a><br />\n<a title=\"Healing Is a Choice\" href=\"https://store.newlife.com/search?searchText=Healing%20Is%20a%20Choice\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Healing Is a Choice</a></p>\n<p><em>Subscribe to the NEW LIFE LIVE! podcast via <a title=\"iTunes\" href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/new-life/id310317904\">iTunes</a> or download the <a title=\"New Life Ministries App\" href=\"http://get.theapp.co/bd32/\">New Life Ministries App</a>.</em></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://newlife.com/new-life-live-october-18-2022/\">New Life Live: October 18, 2022</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://newlife.com\">New Life</a>.</p>\n",
